{"tid":2226593,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"辛祖來到　要光復　這曼聯","createTime":"2020-10-02T06:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T09:18:55.000Z","uid":35348,"like":14,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ec00ce3b417ee0dbe7949f96c575ca80d4a0d8","tid":2226593,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"何以　奧脫福　淚再流<br />\n何以　令曼聯　亦憤恨<br />\n木狗　拒默沉　吶喊聲　響透<br />\n盼辛祖　歸於　這裡<br />\n<br />\n何以　連加特　踢不走<br />\n何以　麥佳亞　從沒退後<br />\n何解　八千萬　但派膠聲　響透<br />\n建自由　光輝　曼聯<br />\n<br />\n在英超　墜落　徬徨午夜<br />\n球場裡　最遠處吹來　哨子聲<br />\n捍曼聯　來齊集這裡　來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣　智慧　也永不滅<br />\n<br />\n辛祖來到　要光復　這曼聯<br />\n曼聯兒女　為冠軍　時代革命<br />\n祈求　獎杯與買人　萬世都不朽<br />\n我願辛祖歸曼聯"},{"pid":"09da57e7588ab96482771c6c3fae7080cb968d3c","tid":2226593,"uid":201604,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"你一出世就係聾人？"},{"pid":"7e8948ce1289fdedf8adcb65e3471ee78cf3a72d","tid":2226593,"uid":363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:14:05.000Z","msg":"何wayne 奧脫福 淚再流<br />\n何wayne 令曼聯 亦憤恨"},{"pid":"7325a06e71ff6e880a8a75a12b7da074b3df8412","tid":2226593,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7df3196a79d722564f0fb178f67dbed4a1e13f","tid":2226593,"uid":1019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:22:29.000Z","msg":"無間道？"},{"pid":"829d414d1432e7d2cc88bd46f195eede138e7631","tid":2226593,"uid":367051,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T06:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2600ecc24e46f5f5b06efd9cd80f1f27d0c22f5e","tid":2226593,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7325a06e71ff6e880a8a75a12b7da074b3d